          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0378P0_20020116_WH_45' title='Link to this speech by Dr Alan Whitehead' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/dr-alan-whitehead" title="Dr Alan Whitehead">Dr. Whitehead</a></cite>
          <p class='first-para'>
